the Sacred Blood Sect had not harmed any civilians.

20
00:02:22,460 --> 00:02:24,329
The claim that they used commoners

21
00:02:24,329 --> 00:02:26,450
to practice the Blood Technique was completely fabricated.

22
00:02:26,450 --> 00:02:27,329
Bai.

23
00:02:27,829 --> 00:02:28,610
I don't know

24
00:02:28,610 --> 00:02:30,670
where you heard such things,

25
00:02:30,750 --> 00:02:31,550
but

26
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:33,600
all five of my juniors died from Blood Technique,

27
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:37,060
and their deaths were gruesome.

28
00:02:38,620 --> 00:02:40,880
Injuries and deaths are inevitable during conflicts.

29
00:02:40,880 --> 00:02:42,660
How can you be so certain

30
00:02:42,990 --> 00:02:44,920
that the Sacred Blood Sect is evil?

31
00:02:46,390 --> 00:02:48,700
[Episode 27]

32
00:02:51,230 --> 00:02:53,630
The most terrifying aspect of Blood Technique

33
00:02:53,630 --> 00:02:56,760
is that practitioners advance rapidly in their skills,

34
00:02:57,160 --> 00:03:00,670
but the longer they practice, the more damage it does to themselves.

35
00:03:00,670 --> 00:03:03,990
