42
00:03:17,550 --> 00:03:19,280
or it will bring trouble to you.

43
00:03:20,510 --> 00:03:21,310
I understand.

44
00:03:22,490 --> 00:03:23,510
In the whole Xiling,

45
00:03:23,510 --> 00:03:25,000
