come at me.

118
00:07:08,830 --> 00:07:11,800
My disciples know nothing.

119
00:07:12,010 --> 00:07:13,850
This is not up to you.

120
00:07:13,870 --> 00:07:15,160
Bastard!

121
00:07:18,520 --> 00:07:19,950
Don't you know

122
00:07:19,980 --> 00:07:23,060
