125
00:07:28,610 --> 00:07:29,510
Master.

126
00:07:29,760 --> 00:07:31,230
You've always wanted to know

127
00:07:31,230 --> 00:07:33,030
where Ruan Siqiong went, right?

128
00:07:33,430 --> 00:07:34,750
