129
00:07:35,970 --> 00:07:37,050
He's dead.

130
00:07:38,140 --> 00:07:38,730
He died giving the Black Wood Human-shaped Sword

131
00:07:38,730 --> 00:07:41,250
to Gu Qingqiao.

132
00:07:42,120 --> 00:07:43,560
He's not coming back.

133
00:07:43,820 --> 00:07:44,830
Impossible.

134
00:07:45,090 --> 00:07:47,090
Siqiong is the best in the world.

135
00:07:47,780 --> 00:07:49,120
He wouldn't die.

136
00:07:49,290 --> 00:07:49,900
Master.

137
00:07:51,100 --> 00:07:53,630
Do you know Ruan Siqiong became the number one

138
00:07:54,340 --> 00:07:55,740
because he gave his heart

139
00:07:56,440 --> 00:07:59,520
to Black Wood Human-shaped Sword?

140
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:02,080
And now that sword is pierced

141
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:04,910
by my Soul-stealing Nail.

142
00:08:05,210 --> 00:08:07,320
No matter how powerful he is,

143
00:08:07,440 --> 00:08:08,490
his soul

144
00:08:08,860 --> 00:08:10,390
will be trapped by me,

145
00:08:10,540 --> 00:08:12,510
forever unable to rise again.

146
00:08:13,790 --> 00:08:14,620
Master.

147
00:08:14,950 --> 00:08:16,030
In my heart,

148
00:08:16,230 --> 00:08:17,900
I still see you as my master.

149
00:08:18,170 --> 00:08:19,770
You are the only one in Xiling

150
00:08:20,300 --> 00:08:21,580
who treats me well

151
00:08:23,040 --> 00:08:24,680
and cares about me.

152
00:08:25,150 --> 00:08:26,270
Bai...

153
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:28,280
Submit to the Sacred Blood Sect.

154
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:30,520
As long as you join us,

155
00:08:31,210 --> 00:08:32,809
I can spare your life.

156
00:08:33,289 --> 00:08:35,799
Do you still remember the Xiling rules?

157
00:08:36,760 --> 00:08:38,480
Xiling disciples

158
00:08:38,890 --> 00:08:40,760
stand united,

159
00:08:41,280 --> 00:08:43,360
watching out for each other.

160
00:08:46,710 --> 00:08:49,230
My greatest regret in life

161
00:08:50,990 --> 00:08:52,630
is not being able

162
00:08:52,650 --> 00:08:55,580
to protect my disciples.

163
00:09:01,270 --> 00:09:04,270
I will never submit to the Sacred Blood Sect.

164
00:09:11,600 --> 00:09:12,500
Zhang Sifeng!

165
00:09:14,690 --> 00:09:16,290
Don't you care about your disciple's life?

166
00:09:16,290 --> 00:09:17,320
Tianshan!

167
00:09:20,880 --> 00:09:22,070
Master!

168
00:09:27,750 --> 00:09:28,550
Master.

169
00:09:29,320 --> 00:09:30,920
It's all my fault.

170
00:09:30,950 --> 00:09:33,750
I failed to see through him.

171
00:09:34,550 --> 00:09:35,510
Tianshan.

172
00:09:35,780 --> 00:09:37,580
What about the other disciples?

173
00:09:39,280 --> 00:09:40,580
I never thought

174
00:09:40,620 --> 00:09:42,630
that among Xiling disciples,

175
00:09:42,740 --> 00:09:45,610
there would be one from the Sacred Blood Sect.

176
00:09:45,890 --> 00:09:49,020
Such disgrace!

177
00:09:49,130 --> 00:09:50,730
You're wrong, Zhang Sifeng

178
00:09:50,750 --> 00:09:52,750
I was born a member of the Sacred Blood Sect.

179
00:09:52,750 --> 00:09:54,280
I joined Xiling Sect

180
00:09:54,300 --> 00:09:56,900
just to get the Black Wood Human-shaped Sword.

181
00:09:57,110 --> 00:09:58,360
In my heart,

182
00:09:58,480 --> 00:10:01,080
