190
00:10:36,620 --> 00:10:37,540
Do you hear me?

191
00:10:41,260 --> 00:10:42,320
Don't make a sound.

192
00:10:46,830 --> 00:10:48,630
So, there's still someone left.

193
00:10:48,680 --> 00:10:49,870
