194
00:10:49,870 --> 00:10:50,550
No!

195
00:10:50,740 --> 00:10:51,430
No!

196
00:10:52,440 --> 00:10:53,350
No!

197
00:10:53,540 --> 00:10:54,580
You should

198
00:10:54,740 --> 00:10:55,940
