201
00:11:05,310 --> 00:11:06,750
A true remnant

202
00:11:07,420 --> 00:11:09,910
of the Sacred Blood Sect.

203
00:11:09,950 --> 00:11:10,750
That's right.

204
00:11:11,390 --> 00:11:12,820
Years ago, the Duan family joined forces

205
00:11:12,820 --> 00:11:16,300
