206
00:11:16,300 --> 00:11:17,370
I was the only one

207
00:11:18,050 --> 00:11:19,410
who escaped.

208
00:11:19,870 --> 00:11:21,000
Great Master Zhang.

209
00:11:21,050 --> 00:11:22,630
