250
00:13:45,980 --> 00:13:47,590
If I can't have it,

251
00:13:48,810 --> 00:13:50,570
no one can.

252
00:13:50,720 --> 00:13:51,380
Yes.

253
00:13:53,490 --> 00:13:54,250
Master.

254
00:13:55,330 --> 00:13:56,650
Our fate

255
00:13:57,370 --> 00:13:58,930
