256
00:13:59,340 --> 00:14:01,900
I will take back everything I've lost.

257
00:14:02,800 --> 00:14:04,560
No one can stop me.

258
00:14:07,010 --> 00:14:07,720
My Lord.

259
00:14:11,240 --> 00:14:12,370
